headline: Okta Set to Join S&P MidCap 400
summary: Okta Inc. (NASD: OKTA) will replace Berry Global Group Inc. (NYSE: BERY) in the S&P MidCap 400 effective prior to the opening of trading on Thursday, May 1. S&P 500 constituent Amcor plc (NYSE: AMCR) is acquiring Berry Global Group in a deal expected to close soon, pending final closing conditions.

headline: Wall Street's First High-Profile Stock Split of 2025 Has Been Announced -- and It's Not Meta Platforms, Netflix, or Costco!
summary: The first prominent stock-split stock of 2025 has skyrocketed 4,500% since its last forward split two decades ago.
